Detailed Description

A class which converts legacy browfileIdentifier strings into equivalent Browid objects.

Overview

A browfile is uniquely identified by either by its legacy browfileIdentifier, although other supplemental data (aliasData, browserName) is needed for some types.  This class provides a method for creating a new Browid object from this identifier and supplemental data.

A browid with the same identification as the given data, or nil if enough nonambiguous data to make a useable browfile could not be extracted.
